OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FTwo stuffed lions, a Lego set and some
OL,7,Fexpensive football boots were among
OL,8,Fthe items taken in the "heist" that
OL,9,Fhit England on the way to their World
OL,10,FCup base in Kansas City.
OL,12,FHaving enjoyed a smooth, injury-free
OL,13,Fwarm-weather training camp in Florida,
OL,14,Fthe Football Association had to deal
OL,15,Fwith an unexpected headache in the
OL,16,FMidwest on Friday night.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@^O]
