OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781504275
OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FEquipment was discovered missing upon
OL,7,Farriving at their Swope Soccer Village
OL,8,Fbase, with Kansas City mayor Quinton
OL,9,FLucas saying "local, state and
OL,10,Ffederal" officials were working on the
OL,11,F"heist in transit of English national
OL,12,Fteam equipment".
OL,14,FJackson County prosecutor Melesa
OL,15,FJohnson has charged two men in
OL,16,Fconnection with the incident, with
OL,17,FMustafa Salik and Erfan Kamal each
OL,18,Ffacing a count of receiving stolen
OL,19,Fproperty, carrying up to seven years
OL,20,Fin prison.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@HO]sD@AOUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
