OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781504275
OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FThe pair drove the England team's
OL,7,Fequipment from their warm-weather
OL,8,Ffacility in West Palm Beach to Kansas
OL,9,FCity, and a detective recovered an
OL,10,Festimated $18,145.41 (#13,530) worth
OL,11,Fof items.
OL,13,FCourt documents show four pairs of
OL,14,F#250 boots and five pairs of #170
OL,15,Fshoes were allegedly found, along with
OL,16,Fsome signed national team shirts, a
OL,17,F#160 World Cup ball and a pair of #120
OL,18,Fgoalkeeper gloves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781504275
OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FTwo stuffed lions and a Lego set of a
OL,7,FNike Air shoe were among the variety
OL,8,Fof other items.
OL,10,FThe FA indicated earlier on Saturday
OL,11,Fthat most of the training gear had
OL,12,Fbeen recovered ahead of the first
OL,13,Fsession at Swope Soccer Village.
OL,15,FEngland back-up goalkeeper Dean
OL,16,FHenderson said with a smile when asked
OL,17,Fif his boots and gloves made it to
OL,18,FKansas City: "Yeah, thankfully. I
OL,19,Fthink they got stolen but we got them
OL,20,Fback so it's all good."
OL,26,@zD@NOU|D@WO]
