OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FExperienced defender Dan Burn found
OL,7,Fout about the incident through the
OL,8,Fmedia reports, joking he "wouldn't be
OL,9,Fable to move very much" if his boots
OL,10,Fhad not turned up.
OL,12,F"We've not made a big deal out of it,"
OL,13,Fhe said. "I've got everything I need,
OL,14,Fso I'm quite happy.
OL,16,F"We know that stuff has been left to
OL,17,Fthe police and as a group we've not
OL,18,Freally spoken about that at all."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@WO]tD@AOUtD@fO]uD@JOUxD@AOUzD@
OL,26,AaO]
