OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAsked if the FA had spoken to the
OL,12,Fplayers, Burn added: "To be honest,
OL,13,Fit's not really been spoken about, so
OL,14,FI think that shows for us that they're
OL,15,Fnot too worried about it as well.
OL,17,F"We're here to train. The first day
OL,18,Fout here, so it's not disrupted our
OL,19,Fpreparation."
OL,26,@tD@VOUyD@AOU{D@MO]
