OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781504275
OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FEngland kick-off their World Cup
OL,7,Fcampaign against Croatia on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fand Kansas City mayor Lucas said: "I
OL,9,Fam grateful for the quick work of the
OL,10,FKansas City Police Department and the
OL,11,FProsecutor's Office in resolving an
OL,12,Finvestigation across several states,
OL,13,Fhelping crime victims recover goods
OL,14,Fstolen in transit, and ensuring the
OL,15,Faccused will face prosecution.
OL,17,F"Kansas City's public safety
OL,18,Fleadership will continue to ensure all
OL,19,Fare safe and offenders will be held
OL,20,Faccountable swiftly for any
OL,21,Fmisconduct."
OL,26,@pD@cOUyD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
