FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781504275
OL,3,CTwo men charged in US over theft of
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup training equipment
OL,6,FJackson County prosecutor Johnson
OL,7,Fadded: "Jackson County will not
OL,8,Ftolerate any criminal activity that
OL,9,Ftargets World Cup visitors, including
OL,10,Fthe international teams that have
OL,11,Ftravelled here to compete.
OL,13,F"We thank the Kansas City Police
OL,14,FDepartment and our on-call attorneys
OL,15,Ffor their quick work investigating
OL,16,Fthis incident and filing charges
OL,17,Fimmediately. Our office is committed
OL,18,Fto holding these individuals
OL,19,Faccountable."
OL,26,@oD@HOUuD@AOU{D@MO]
